### 🔥 Featured Projects

#### 🏢 [Decentralized Real-Estate Marketplace](https://github.com/muhlikVision/Decentralized-Real-Estate-Marketplace)
A full-stack Web3 application tokenizing physical properties as ERC-721 NFTs. Features robust smart contracts for automated escrow, decentralized IPFS storage for immutable data, and a custom Python API streaming AI-driven property valuations directly to a ReactJS frontend.

#### 🛡️ [Scam Checker: Threat Intelligence App](https://github.com/muhlikVision/Scam-Checker)
A highly responsive platform built to proactively identify phishing and scam threats. Integrates the Google Gemini API to analyze user-uploaded screenshots and text, generating structured JSON risk assessments logged securely in a PostgreSQL database via SQLAlchemy.

#### 🚗 [CARFARE: AI-Integrated Smart Parking](https://github.com/muhlikVision/CARFARE)
A cross-platform mobile and web application built with Flutter and Dart. Utilizes Firebase for real-time data syncing and parking allocation logic, and integrates Google ML Kit for real-time optical character recognition (OCR) of vehicle license plates directly on the edge.

